* 鎖頭（Lock）
* 驚嚇（Shock）
* 桶裝（Barrel）

== 評價 ==
《聖誕夜驚魂》收穫了多數影評人的好評。根據[[爛蕃茄|爛蕃茄]]上收集的90篇專業影評文章，其中85篇給出了「新鮮」的正面評價，「新鮮度」為94%，平均得分8.2分（滿分10分）<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/nightmare_before_christmas/ | title = The Nightmare Before Christmas | work = [[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] | accessdate = 2014-10-13 | archive-date = 2021-02-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210223144130/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/nightmare_before_christmas | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

影評人[[羅傑·伊伯特|羅傑·伊伯特]]給予了本片積極的評價，伊伯特認為《聖誕夜驚魂》的視覺效果與《[[星際大戰四部曲：曙光乍現|星際大戰]]》一樣具有革命性，且表示電影「充滿想像力，帶給我們一個全新的世界。」<ref>{{cite news | title = The Nightmare Before Christmas | url = http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/19931022/REVIEWS/310220302/1023 | work = [[Roger_Ebert|Roger Ebert]].com | date = 1993-10-22 | accessdate = 2008-09-26 | archive-date = 2012-10-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121008100720/http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F19931022%2FREVIEWS%2F310220302%2F1023 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

== 榮譽 ==
電影被提名至[[奧斯卡最佳視覺效果獎|奧斯卡最佳視覺效果獎]]和{{link-en|雨果獎最佳戲劇表現|Hugo Award for Best Dramatic Presentation}}<ref>{{cite web | work = [[Internet_Movie_Database|Internet Movie Database]] | url = http://www.imdb.com/Sections/Awards/Academy_Awards_USA/1994 | title = 66th Academy Awards | accessdate = 2008-09-26 | archive-date = 2009-01-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090117024813/http://www.imdb.com/Sections/Awards/Academy_Awards_USA/1994 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | work = [[Internet_Movie_Database|Internet Movie Database]] | url = http://www.imdb.com/Sections/Awards/Hugo_Awards/1994 | title = Hugo Awards: 1994 | accessdate = 2008-09-26 | archive-date = 2004-11-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20041120234647/http://www.imdb.com/Sections/Awards/Hugo_Awards/1994 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。《聖誕夜驚魂》獲得了[[土星獎最佳奇幻電影得獎列表|土星獎最佳奇幻電影]]，而葉夫曼則贏得{{link-en|土星獎最佳音樂獎|Saturn Award for Best Music|最佳音樂獎}}<ref>{{cite web | work = [[Internet_Movie_Database|Internet Movie Database]] | url = http://www.imdb.com/Sections/Awards/Academy_of_Science_Fiction_Fantasy_And_Horror_Films_USA/1994 | title = Saturn Awards: 1994 | accessdate = 2008-09-26 | archive-date = 2009-03-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090305111727/http://www.imdb.com/Sections/Awards/Academy_of_Science_Fiction_Fantasy_And_Horror_Films_USA/1994 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。葉夫曼還被提名[[金球獎最佳電影配樂|最佳電影配樂]]<ref>{{cite web | work = [[Internet_Movie_Database|Internet Movie Database]] | url = http://www.imdb.com/Sections/Awards/Golden_Globes_USA/1994 | title = 51st Golden Globe Awards | accessdate = 2008-09-26 | archive-date = 2008-12-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081224033006/http://www.imdb.com/Sections/Awards/Golden_Globes_USA/1994 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。該電影還被提名2008年，由[[美國電影學會|美國電影學會]]評選的[[AFI十大類型十大佳片|AFI十大類型十大佳片]]中，但未能入選<ref>{{cite web|url=http://connect.afi.com/site/DocServer/10top10.pdf?docID=381&AddInterest=1781 |title=AFI's 10 Top 10 Nominees |format=PDF |date= |accessdate=2016-08-19 |deadurl=bot: unknown |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110716071937/http://connect.afi.com/site/DocServer/10top10.pdf?docID=381&AddInterest=1781 |archivedate=2011-07-16 }}</ref>。

